:"Poppins-Medium","family":"Poppins","style":"Medium","size":25}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"area","width":920,"height":685},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":26,"from":0,"to":67,"x":0}],[{"y":64,"from":67,"to":134,"x":0}],[{"y":102,"from":134,"to":208,"x":0}],[{"y":140,"from":208,"to":279,"x":0}],[{"y":178,"from":279,"to":339,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":216,"from":340,"to":410,"x":0}],[{"y":254,"from":410,"to":481,"x":0}],[{"y":292,"from":481,"to":553,"x":0}],[{"y":330,"from":553,"to":618,"x":0}],[{"y":368,"from":618,"to":654,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":406,"from":655,"to":720,"x":0}],[{"y":444,"from":720,"to":792,"x":0}],[{"y":482,"from":792,"to":861,"x":0}],[{"y":520,"from":861,"to":933,"x":0}],[{"y":558,"from":933,"to":969,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":596,"from":970,"to":1045,"x":0}],[{"y":634,"from":1045,"to":1120,"x":0}],[{"y":672,"from":1120,"to":1181,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"Eliconsult is a specialized B2B real estate consultancy supporting corporate clients, developers, investment firms, and institutional partners across the region. Based in Dubai, we provide strategic advisory services, market intelligence, and tailored solutions designed to help businesses make informed, data-driven real estate decisions.\nTo enhance efficiency for our partners, we developed FILFLEX, a smart digital portal that streamlines the process of locating specific units across all major developers. FILFLEX enables corporate teams to filter, compare, and access property data instantly, improving accuracy, speed, and operational productivity.\nOur expertise spans residential and commercial project analysis, developer coordination, portfolio evaluation, and corporate acquisition strategies. We work exclusively with businesses, offering structured insights and professional guidance that align with organizational goals and long-term investment strategies.\nAt Eliconsult, we believe that real estate advisory should be transparent, analytical, and results-driven. Our commitment is to build strong, lasting partnerships based on trust, expertise, and measurable value."}}]}},{"type":"shape","name":"Rectangle 35","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_RECTANGLE","constraintLeft":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3234}}},"id":"b649053e-3e62-4904-abcc-99605ccd38b0","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3234},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":17,"g":34,"b":80}}},"stroke":{"type":"none","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":112,"g":112,"b":112}},"width":1,"align":"inside"}},"shape":{"type":"rect","x":0,"y":0,"width":1920,"height":759}},{"type":"shape","name":"Rectangle 99","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_RECTANGLE","constraintLeft":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":7484}}},"id":"e430470a-698d-4ac9-963b-7fdb78c637d9","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":7484},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":17,"g":34,"b":80}}},"stroke":{"type":"none","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":112,"g":112,"b":112}},"width":1,"align":"inside"}},"shape":{"type":"rect","x":0,"y":0,"width":1920,"height":500}},{"type":"shape","name":"Rectangle 22","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_RECTANGLE","constraintWidth":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":1450,"ty":3567}}},"id":"20aa15cc-3aaa-4f16-b820-be377519f150","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":1450,"ty":3567},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":255,"g":255,"b":255}}},"stroke":{"type":"none","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":112,"g":112,"b":112}},"width":1,"align":"inside"},"filters":[{"type":"dropShadow","global":true,"params":{"dropShadows":[{"dx":0,"dy":0,"r":5,"color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":17,"g":34,"b":80},"alpha":0.4}}]}}]},"visualBounds":{"x":1435,"y":3552,"width":430,"height":380},"shape":{"type":"rect","x":0,"y":0,"width":400