al estate marketing designed exclusively for corporate clients, developers, investment firms, and institutional partners. Our approach focuses on delivering structured, data-driven marketing solutions that support large-scale decision-making and enhance the visibility of real estate projects across the professional ecosystem.\n\n. Strategic positioning and competitive analysis\n. Tailored messaging for corporate audiences\n. Market intelligence and developer insights integration\n. FILFLEX-powered property discovery for corporate teams\n. Partnership strengthening and sales team support\n"}},{"type":"group","name":"Group 117","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintLeft":true,"constraintWidth":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3827}}},"id":"7661e535-5f38-46b6-aee2-4a3fe32fe2b6","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3827},"group":{"children":[{"type":"text","name":"UAE Project Training & Presentation","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintWidth":true,"constraintHeight":true,"singleTextObject":true,"rangedStyles":[{"length":27,"linkId":"","fontFamily":"Poppins","fontStyle":"Bold","postscriptName":"Poppins-Bold","fontSize":30,"charSpacing":0,"underline":false,"textTransform":"none","textScript":"none","fill":{"value":4283072423},"strikethrough":false,"hyperlinkUrl":""}]}},"id":"929c2528-7e9d-42dd-8ec3-f30b3672b8ad","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":97,"ty":1282},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":74,"g":127,"b":167}}},"font":{"postscriptName":"Poppins-Bold","family":"Poppins","style":"Bold","size":30},"textAttributes":{"lineHeight":30}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"autoHeight","width":679},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":32,"from":0,"to":35,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"UAE Project Training & Presentation"}},{"type":"text","name":"Eliconsult provides specialized UAE Project Training and Presentation services designed exclusively for corporate teams, brokerages, investment firms, and real estate professionals. Our training programs deliver structured, developer-aligned knowledge that","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintWidth":true,"constraintHeight":true,"singleTextObject":true,"rangedStyles":[{"length":27,"linkId":"","fontFamily":"Poppins","fontStyle":"Regular","postscriptName":"Poppins-Regular","fontSize":20,"charSpacing":0,"underline":false,"textTransform":"none","textScript":"none","fill":{"value":4279312976},"strikethrough":false,"hyperlinkUrl":""}]}},"id":"35e8c3c3-51e5-455a-bcf3-a2d2b2a27794","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":97,"ty":1341},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":17,"g":34,"b":80}}},"font":{"postscriptName":"Poppins-Regular","family":"Poppins","style":"Regular","size":20}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"autoHeight","width":893},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":21,"from":0,"to":88,"x":0}],[{"y":51,"from":88,"to":167,"x":0}],[{"y":81,"from":167,"to":252,"x":0}],[{"y":111,"from":252,"to":337,"x":0}],[{"y":141,"from":337,"to":353,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":171,"from":354,"to":354,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":201,"from":355,"to":425,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":231,"from":426,"to":481,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":261,"from":482,"to":537,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":291,"from":538,"to":591,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":321,"from":592,"to":643,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"Eliconsult provides specialized UAE Project Training and Presentation services designed exclusively for corporate teams, brokerages, investment firms, and real estate professionals. Our training programs deliver structured, developer-aligned knowledge that empowers organizations to confidently present, promote, and sell major UAE real estate projects.\n\n. Comprehensive modules on master communities and developer portfolios\n. Project specifications, unit mixes, and payment plans\n. Sales-focused and strategic positioning presentations\n. Staff onboarding and internal knowledge enhancement\n. Real-time unit access via FILFLEX during sessions"}}]}},{"type":"group","name":"Group 118","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintWidth":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":54,"ty":3847}}},"id":"ad9b9b48-0593-4ce1-82e3-8fc422dcfc53","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":54,"ty":3847},"group":{"children":[{"type":"text","name":"FILFLEX: Smart Property-Search Engine","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintWidth":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"singleTextObject":true,"rangedStyles":[{"length":27,"linkId":"","fontFamily":"Poppins","fontStyle":"Bold","postscriptName":"Poppins-Bold","fontSize":30,"charSpacing":0,"underline":false,"textTransform":"none","textScript":"none","fill":{"value":4283072423},"strikethrough":false,"hyperlinkUrl":""}]}},"id":"0c8015a6-556e-4e7c-b965-2564251b0fb6","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":874,"ty":1978},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":74,"g":127,"b":167}}},"font":{"postscriptName":"Poppins-Bold","family":"Poppins","style":"Bold","size":30},"textAttributes":{"lineHeight":30}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"autoHeight","width":749},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":32,"from":0,"to":37,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"FILFLEX: Smart Property-Search Engine"}},{"type":"text","name":"FILFLEX is a proprietary digital platform developed by Eliconsult to streamline and accelerate property discovery for corporate clients. Built specifically for B2B use, FILFLEX centralizes inventory from all major developers, allowing businesses to locate ","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintWidth":true,"constraintRight":true,"constraintHeight":true,"singleTextObject":true,"rangedStyles":[{"length":27,"linkId":"","fontFamily":"Poppins","fontStyle":"Regular","postscriptName":"Poppins-Regular","fontSize":20,"charSpacing":0,"underline":false,"textTransform":"none","textScript":"none","fill":{"value":4283072423},"strikethrough":false,"hyperlinkUrl":""}]}},"id":"6763f55b-1c86-4b32-8088-727ecb6ef954","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":874,"ty":2047},"style":{"fill":{"type":"solid","color":{"mode":"RGB","value":{"r":74,"g":127,"b":167}}},"font":{"postscriptName":"Poppins-Regular","family":"Poppins","style":"Regular","size":20}},"text":{"frame":{"type":"autoHeight","width":922},"paragraphs":[{"lines":[[{"y":21,"from":0,"to":95,"x":0}],[{"y":51,"from":95,"to":189,"x":0}],[{"y":81,"from":189,"to":276,"x":0}],[{"y":111,"from":276,"to":305,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":141,"from":306,"to":306,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":171,"from":307,"to":397,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":201,"from":398,"to":479,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":231,"from":480,"to":541,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":261,"from":542,"to":587,"x":0}]]},{"lines":[[{"y":291,"from":588,"to":656,"x":0}]]}],"rawText":"FILFLEX is a proprietary digital platform developed by Eliconsult to streamline and accelerate property discovery for corporate clients. Built specifically for B2B use, FILFLEX centralizes inventory from all major developers, allowing businesses to locate specific units with unmatched speed and accuracy.\n\n. Unified developer inventory — access property data from multiple developers in one place\n. Advanced filtering — search by unit type, size, layout, price, and availability\n. Instant side-by-side comparisons for faster decision-making\n. Real-time updated data for maximum accuracy\n. Reduced manual search time and eliminated developer back-and-forth"}}]}},{"type":"group","name":"Group 119","meta":{"ux":{"nameL10N":"SHAPE_GROUP","constraintLeft":true,"constraintWidth":true,"constraintHeight":true,"localTransform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3863.0625}}},"id":"7092e6c2-9704-46da-bd0f-1427fa556b7a","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":0,"ty":3863.0625},"group":{"children":[{"type":"group","name":"Logo","id":"db0a734c-3f4d-42a3-8cc8-1fb91029e515","transform":{"a":1,"b":0,"c":0,"d":1,"tx":354.83837890625,"ty":1974.9375},"meta":{"ux":{"hasCustomName":true,"